node.text:
For all of us that stopped while packing Yumbox for our child & asked ourselves why I can’t get nice packed lunches like this - full of variety and color. Yes, you can get your own Yumbox. We all deserve one 🙃

Repost @candishes.kitchen
・・・
Mom confession, while I love making cute bentos and snacks for my kids, I always forget to make myself something when we go on outings! Every.single.time! Who’s with me? It goes to show that momma’s always put their kids first above anything else! But we always need to remember to feed ourselves too! It’s so important! Mom tip: get yourself a bento box and while you’re making your kids one, you have no more excuses to forget about yourself anymore because you have one too! 

Today I’m sharing my own snacking bento box for my 12 hr shift! I’d like to call this my charcuterie style bento: 

☀️ granola bear
☀️ cherries
☀️ strawberries
☀️ bison salami
☀️ balsamic vinegar triscuits and cheese
☀️ kalamata olives 
☀️ mixed nuts and fruit 

#bentoboxlunch #bentobox #momlife #mommyssnacks #snacksonsnacks #allmine #yumbox #canadianmom #foodoftheday #foodofinstagram #chacuterie #yumboxlunch #shiftworker #packedlunch #snacksarelife #nursesofinstagram #treatyourself #backtoschool #healthylifestyle

We are proud to work with so many small businesses worldwide. Times are hard, but by supporting each other we will get to the other side stronger than ever. ✨
